WEBVTT

00:00:05.234 --> 00:00:08.279 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Courage isn’t something that comes easy.

00:00:09.405 --> 00:00:12.658 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I suddenly felt really insecure and afraid.

00:00:13.367 --> 00:00:16.370 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Everyone was against me.

00:00:17.830 --> 00:00:21.876 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I knew that no matter what,
this was going to hurt my family.

00:00:22.835 --> 00:00:26.881 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Inside, I just feel broken.

00:00:27.798 --> 00:00:31.844 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was like having Goliath in front of me.

00:00:32.887 --> 00:00:37.641 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah said
that “they will certainly fight against you,

00:00:38.350 --> 00:00:40.978 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but they will not prevail against you,
for ‘I am with you.’”

00:00:42.563 --> 00:00:47.109 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Be courageous and strong and go to work.”

00:00:48.444 --> 00:00:52.072 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“I will fortify you, yes, I will help you.”

00:00:52.907 --> 00:00:56.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Take your position, stand still,

00:00:56.535 --> 00:00:59.788 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and see the salvation of Jehovah in your behalf.”

